title: Vox Pops Presents 1990s [2009] DVD5
description: Vox Pops Presents 1990s [2009] DVD5 Warner UK's Vox Pops Presents 1990s pairs a CD of hits with a DVD of videos for those same singles, offering a nifty little aural and visual time capsule. As it happens, this particular time capsule skews very heavily toward the dance-pop side of the '90s. These aren't necessarily the biggest hits of the '90s, but they do add up to an entertaining snapshot of the British mainstream of the decade.
